08:02.699 --> 08:05.131
Steven!

08:25.728 --> 08:29.692
Pearl!
Pearl, you have to tell me

08:29.726 --> 08:33.562
- what's wrong.
- Sometimes...

08:33.647 --> 08:36.573
you even sound like her.

08:36.927 --> 08:42.238
Do you remember this place?
Do you have any of her memories?

08:42.239 --> 08:49.915
We were right here, over
5,000 years ago.

08:52.979 --> 08:55.050
- Pearl...
- Yes?

08:55.135 --> 08:58.304
...I'm going to stay and
fight for this planet.

08:58.388 --> 09:01.017
You don't have to do this with me.

09:01.052 --> 09:04.093
- But I want to!
- I know you do.

09:04.177 --> 09:09.431
Please, please understand ...
if we lose, we'll be killed,

09:09.482 --> 09:12.484
and if we win,
we can never go home.

09:12.485 --> 09:17.105
Why would I ever want
to go home if you're here?

09:22.078 --> 09:27.116
- My Pearl.
- You're wonderful.

09:31.418 --> 09:36.091
Everything I ever did, I did for her.
Now she's gone...

09:36.176 --> 09:42.431
but I'm still here.
Sometimes I wonder

09:42.465 --> 09:46.184
if she can see me through
your eyes.

09:46.219 --> 09:48.697
What would she think of me now?

09:54.144 --> 09:58.264
Well, I think
you're pretty great.

